{title: Span Markup}

{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[G]Roses are <span foreground="red">red</span>
[C]Violets are <span foreground="blue">blue</span>
[D]Sugar is <span foreground="white">white</span>
[G]And so are [C]you
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_chorus}
[C]<span foreground="green">Green with envy</span>
[G]<span foreground="gold">Golden memories</span>
[D]<span foreground="purple">Purple mountains</span>
[G]<span foreground="orange">Orange skies</span>
{end_of_chorus}
